Sentencas: La(Sr)MnO3 cathodes have been investigated as high temperature oxygen reduction electrodes in the solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: HIGH-PERFORMANCE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL CATHODE FABRICATED BY ELECTROCHEMICAL VAPOR-DEPOSITION

Sentencas: The cathodes consist of 10 mole percent of yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) thin film electrolyte layer deposited on a porous La0.81Sr0.09MnO3 tube using the electrochemical vapor deposition method.
Titulo: HIGH-PERFORMANCE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL CATHODE FABRICATED BY ELECTROCHEMICAL VAPOR-DEPOSITION

Sentencas: The La(Sr)KnO3/YSZ cathodes have different electrochemical properties from those fabricated with the sintering method.
Titulo: HIGH-PERFORMANCE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL CATHODE FABRICATED BY ELECTROCHEMICAL VAPOR-DEPOSITION

Sentencas: The cathode polarization was about 1 mV at a current density of 1.5 A/cm2 in oxygen at 1000-degrees-C. This type of cathode has an extremely large phase boundary and large interfacial capacitance (more than 1 F/cm2) which is approximately proportional to the oxygen partial pressure.
Titulo: HIGH-PERFORMANCE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL CATHODE FABRICATED BY ELECTROCHEMICAL VAPOR-DEPOSITION
